<span id="freeTextContainer10353119710285687238">Wallace Earle Stegner was an American historian, novelist, short story writer, and environmentalist. Some call him &quot;The Dean of Western Writers.&quot; He won the Pulitzer Prize in 1972 and the U.S. National Book Award in 1977.</span>
  <span id="freeText10353119710285687238" style="display:none">Wallace Earle Stegner was an American historian, novelist, short story writer, and environmentalist. Some call him "The Dean of Western Writers." He won the Pulitzer Prize in 1972 and the U.S. National Book Award in 1977.</span>
